{"tid":1439051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"超合作運動 -  萬人有秩序去警局申請盂蘭節燒街衣","createTime":"2019-08-10T03:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T03:52:52.000Z","uid":281193,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8c3c03bd47e1656c5ffb4d81a1e8cc8e1712f064","tid":1439051,"uid":281193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:40:51.000Z","msg":"下星期三就係七月十四盂蘭節，燒街衣係香港傳統文化，有鑑於近日社會太多衝突，所以出來燒街衣，最好先取得警方嘅不反對通知書，做良好市民，與警合作。<br />\n<br />\n所以，大家應該先响48小時前，即係12/8 星期一，到附近警局申請燒街衣不反對通知書，批唔批都好，都要做好市民嘅義務，千萬不要非法集結，破壞社會安寧。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aca7114a9a118e35e47cf765aab54296ec35823","tid":1439051,"uid":281193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:44:23.000Z","msg":"萬人超合作運動!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7608309cc8a268a536fd91ddf3ee1e78f5f74735","tid":1439051,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:52:52.000Z","msg":"緊急！關於港島東反送中反黑大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}